title: Brain discovery explains a great mystery of Alzheimer's, Parkinson's

title_detail.value: Brain discovery explains a great mystery of Alzheimer's, Parkinson's

summary: One of the great mysteries of neuroscience may finally have an answer: Scientists have identified a potential explanation for the mysterious death of specific brain cells seen in Alzheimer's, Parkinson's and other neurodegenerative diseases.
